defaultHarold M
defaulta
defaultcMillan may be 
defaultmis
defaultquoted in apparently speaking of  
default“events
default,
default dear boy
default,
default events”
default, but there is a reality in
default this that often favours
default 
defaultthe immediate 
defaultrather than 
defaultthe 
defaultemergen
defaultt.
default Yet, considering the 
defaultfuture
default 
defaultcan enable a more 
defaultefficient and effective use of diminishing resources
default,
default which has the potential to gain savings for the tax payer
default. P
defaultolicies that are 
default‘
defaultfuture
default-
defaultproofed
default’
default can be more sustainable and adaptable to changing circumstances, which saves resources. 
defaultFor 
